   * [Spec]s and [io.kotest.core.test.TestCase]s.
   *
   * For example:
   *
   * class ProjectConfig : AbstractProjectConfig() {
   *    override val failOnEmptyTestSuite = true
   *    override val testCaseOrder = TestCaseOrder.Random
   * }
   * ```
   */
